{"tid":512829,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"輪椅界林寶堅尼 隨時切換成像機械人、車子、輪椅的模式","createTime":"2017-12-29T01:58:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T03:56:40.000Z","uid":72478,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"040f4526d0afe7efa0eb17962d376ebc474eeab2","tid":512829,"uid":72478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T01:58:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3018/d3018799.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3018%2Fd3018799.jpg&h=f29c0059&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3018/d3018809.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3018%2Fd3018809.jpg&h=af34ed8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3018/d3018810.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3018%2Fd3018810.jpg&h=a700e2e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRODEM貼心的設計讓使用者可以依靠自身力量做騎乘。　（圖／翻攝自tmsuk株式會社，下同）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為了方便使用者自行乘坐，並減輕看護人員的負擔，日本機器人製造商tmsuk開發出了與從前方坐上去的普通輪椅不同，而是採用了從後方騎乘設計的四輪摩托型電動輪椅RODEM，讓使用者不用改變身體方向，可依靠自己的臂力從床邊或椅子上直接坐上去，還能透過調整座椅，輕鬆完成盥洗、飲食、換乘等動作。<br />\n<br />\n位於京都市的tmsuk研究所發佈的這款RODEM四輪摩托型電動輪椅，全長約1公尺，寬約70公分，重約110公斤，可使用智慧型手機遠程操作，充電一次還能連續行駛15公里左右。<br />\n<br />\ntmsuk公司表示，這款RODEM是為了讓任何人都能在少子高齡化的21世紀中，實現便利生活的社會的全新產品，並且能拓展使用者的生活空間、提升生活品質，此外，還可以根據使用者的意願，隨時切換成機械人、車子、輪椅的模式，是最新型的通用設計式騎乘設備。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/affS1NmsIwg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FaffS1NmsIwg&d=y7lpBltl%2FaEt7Gcm1OWnFpzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=a04bcf38\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/affS1NmsIwg</a><br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20171229/1081370.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20171229%2F1081370.htm&d=y7lpBltl%2FaEt7Gcm1OWnFpzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=643ecf87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20171229/1081370.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇完成條片都搵唔到機械人模式係邊, 係咪指架輪椅會係隔離standby=機械人mode<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64b619afb6b4a12202c4a9d6a4b579945bbdaae4","tid":512829,"uid":1067,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T02:06:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/29/100627_0370133606d6b8a717b95610ba17535b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F29%2F100627_0370133606d6b8a717b95610ba17535b.png&h=a0a18490&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a64ff46588273e8176904bb6b15ed6e75b604ef3","tid":512829,"uid":104658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T02:15:06.000Z","msg":"成部吸塵機咁"},{"pid":"a14e0f75cc85e3e755715862854867c45aa8e706","tid":512829,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T02:18:44.000Z","msg":"無得向後挨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ac0cbdd341ac812ea50df7bb4928986b31a1ae8","tid":512829,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T02:20:15.000Z","msg":"幾時有幫坐輪椅既人行路既支架<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68105a8ba5cb80ea0e416f6114880d4235ebacfb","tid":512829,"uid":91664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T02:21:42.000Z","msg":"有嘢向上屌？"},{"pid":"d01da8119ea9da267aa22e399c8eff8f75b8c3b0","tid":512829,"uid":76753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T02:24:41.000Z","msg":"有冇得放龜"},{"pid":"0f1b099db2117cdba0c9dff739f5c78aa64ad4ff","tid":512829,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T03:03:30.000Z","msg":"冇得挨......."},{"pid":"2ba3b5eabc3aa3c1dfca958e454e952d8301d69d","tid":512829,"uid":35005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T03:50:52.000Z","msg":"冇得挨已經ON9"},{"pid":"3c97acc6ec953485e62